Folk musician http://lisharvey.com  Lis Harvey, holds the http://lisharvey.com/lis/50state.php Guinnessconfirmed record for Fastest to Play A Concert in All 50 States.  Lis set her World Records record by playing 52 shows in all 50 US states in 60 days in 2002. Lis currently resides in Davis, and has played locally at Bistro 33, Delta of Venus and Cafe Roma.
